name: DAYTONA 500
comments: Ricky Stenhouse Jr. has won the DAYTONA 500 at Daytona International Speedway, his third career victory in the NASCAR Cup Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following vehicle(s) dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reason indicated: No. 8 (Backup Car).
